		{
			description: [
				"The &6Kettle&r is a crafting station which allows you to &cbrew tea and other aromatic beverages&r."
				""
				"It is similar to the Cooking Pot, taking&c two items and a bottle as input&r. Where it differs, however, is that it also needs a &cliquid to brew the items into&r."
				""
				"You may&c insert liquid&r using the bottle slot in its UI or by simply right clicking the &6kettle&r.&7 In case you're not familiar with the terminology, 250 mB (milliblocks) is one glass bottle and 1,000 mB is one bucket."
				""
				"Look at the recipes you can use a &6kettle&r for by pressing \"u\"&7 (or the Show Uses key if you changed it)&r on the item in JEI or your inventory."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"{image:kubejs:item/respite_brewing width:258 height:139 align:center fit:true}"
				""
				"On the left is the&c input liquid&r. This recipe requires 1000 mB of milk."
				""
				"The two slots above the fire are the &cinputs&r. This recipe requires one sugar and one cocoa beans."
				""
				"On the bottom is the &ccontainer&r the finished product can be captured in. This recipe (and most others) accept glass bottles."
			]
			id: "5A9395C87DAFFC73"
			rewards: [{
				count: 15
				id: "7B9AE2E3E61C1817"
				item: "lightmanscurrency:coin_copper"
