		{
			dependencies: ["5A9395C87DAFFC73"]
			description: [
				"The &6keg&r is your go-to for&6 fermenting&r, which is the process that primarily results in &cbeverages, cheese, and preserves&r."
				""
				"This is much like &cbrewing tea&r as described earlier, but with some more factors."
				""
				"The first is &ctemperature&r. Each recipe has a&c range of temperatures&r in which it can be made. This is influenced by the&c biome&r you're in, and the presence of &cHeating Casks&r or &cIce Crates&r. "
				""
				"Make sure the &6keg's&r temperature readout &cexactly matches &rthe recipe's requirements."
				""
				"Next, you'll have to plan ahead with &6kegs&r, since they &ctake a long time&r to do their thing: &cbetween 4 and 10 minutes&r depending on the recipe. Don't freak out if the arrow isn't filling; as long as the &cbubbles&r in the UI are animated, your &6keg&r is working."
				""
				"And that's about it! Everything else about the &6keg&r is more or less the same as the&c kettle&r. JEI is once again your best friend for figuring out the recipes."
			]
